      "body" : "> Timezones do not come into play in UTC time as I understand it. So the only difficult problem is to calculate the number of days since start of the epoch.\r\n\r\nCorrect. unix time uses UTC and \"only cares\" about the number of days. Also there seem to be algorithms out there, so we don't have to invent our own. \r\n",
